imdb.plot outline: Fighting game veterans gootecks and Mike Ross take on challenges from online warriors in Street Fighter on Excellent Adventures. This charismatic duo bring their special brand of buddy comedy to a worldwide audience of gamers every week, along with a slew of guest appearances from fighting game luminaries.
imdb.title: The Gootecks & Mike Ross Show
